data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Whispering Trails neighborhood! This exquisite single-story residence boasts 5 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 luxurious bathrooms, providing ample space for your family and guests. The stunning backyard features a private pool with a built-in barbecue and a cabana bath, making outdoor entertaining a breeze. Recent upgrades include a new roof in 2022. This home has a 3-car garage, a convenient split floor plan including a Jack and Jill bath, a beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a cozy fireplace in the living room, this home is designed for both comfort and functionality. and a screened-in patio provides security and comfort, making this property the ultimate oasis for your family. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Whispering Trails gem your forever home!
